Title: The First Muslim
Author: লেসলি হ্যাজেলটন
Summary:
"The FIRST MUSLIM"
Lesley Hazleton reported on the Middle East from Jerusalem for more than a dozen years, and has written for Time, The New York.
Times, The New York Review of Books, and Harper's, among other publications. Her last book, After the Prophet, was a finalist for the PEN-USA Book Award. Hazleton lives in Seattle.
